metadata.name: We awoke together.
metadata.description:
We awoke in a technological dystopia. Phasing(s) creates works by commissioning small pieces of creative from various people on fiverr. Phasing(s) is the editor. He puts the works together to create something new. Embracing the unexpected outcome of how the individual will perceive the brief. 

Phasing(s) Rising is his message.  A meditation on the flatness of the world. The strangeness of our existence.
